name: Vampy Vaporware
description: This artwork was created as part of the #Legato100 project, as a cover art for "Nifty Sax: Genesis #74 - Vampy Vaporware". Legato100 is a collaborative project of 100 artworks for 100 music tracks. The track is available here: https://bit.ly/NiftySax-74. Project's official page: https://niftysax.com/legato100.
